Welcome to the latest version of Xbox Media Center (XBMC) Installer Deluxe.  
The main reason for this release is because of the latest Stable version of XBMC (4XBOX).


Changes since v1.43 (Last ISO Release):
 
Updated: XBMC Application (XBMC4XBOX v3.0.1 STABLE)
Updated: XBMC Scripts, Plugins, and Skins



Use the ISO Updater to integrate any desired addon packs into the
XBMCID ISO and then burn with your favourite CD/DVD Burning Sofware.

If your Xbox is already modded, you can always unpack the finished ISO and FTP it to your Xbox HDD. Copy it to E:AppsXBMCID (or F or G Drive)
